data.description: Your next home awaits you in the heart of Springfield! Secluded neighborhood with convenient shopping and close to universities! This home features 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. Total 1,560 sq ft of living space, this home is ideally situated next to Historic C-Street with easy access to dining, activities, and events. Updates to the home include new stove, dishwasher, shiplap wall in kitchen, high efficiency toilets with bidet, rear exterior doors replaced with inset blinds, main service pipes excavated and new lines reset from home to city main, lots of new landscaping including fencing, garden, rose bushes and elderberry bushes. Schedule a tour today!
